      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kamchr mehs to dsir- \ndejschi/ tad ktua muhfo Stirds \nbailiga/ un newa wairs Droh- \nfehtbas pee Wihreem preekfch \njums/ jo tas KUNGS juhsfu \nDeews irr weens Deews ang- \nfcha Debbes Wirfü/un appakfcha \nwirs Semmes."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nu tad swehrejeet man \njelle pee ta KUNGA/ tapehz/ ka \nes Schehlastibu pee jums efinu \ndarrifusi/ ka arridsan juhs grib- \nbat Schehlastibu darriht pee man- \nna Tehwa Namma / un dohdect \nman weenu ustizzamu Sihni."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka juhs dshwn gribbat \npainest mannu Tehwu/ mannu \nMahti/ un mannu Brahtus/ \nun mannas Mahfas/ ar wiſu \nkas teem peederr/ un ka juhs grib- \nbat muhsas Dwehjeles no Nah- \nwes isglahbt."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad runuaja tee Wihri \nus to: Ja mehs ne darrifim \nSchehlastibu un Peetizzibu pee \ntewis/ kad tas KUNGS mums \ntcho Semmi dohs/ tad lai muh- \nfo Dwehteie juhsfo Weeta mirst/ \nja juhs tcho muhfu Darbu sin- \nnannu ne darriteet."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nolaide winna tohs \nar weenu Wirwi zaur to Lohgu/ \nio winnas Nams bija ne ta Pils- \nbta Muhri/ un winna dshwo- \nus to Muhri."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winna fazzija us teen \nEita Kalnôs/ ka ne jaschu te \nPakkat-Dsinneji juhs fastohp \nun apslepjeetees tur trihs Dec \nnas/ teekains tee Pakkat-Dsin \nnejt atgreesisees / tad eita peh \nfawu Zeltu."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tee Wihri u \nwinnu? Mehs buhſim nenose \ndsigi schinui Swebreschanâ/ tu \nmums eſti likufi swehrecht."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rangi/ kad mehs uhs t \nSemmi nahkam/ tad buhs te \nscho farkann Wirwi pee taw \nLohga peeſect/ ar ko tu muhs ni \nlaidifi/ un few buhs pee tew f \npulzinaht faru Tehwu/ un taw \nMahti/ untawus Brahtus/ u \nwiſu tawa Tehwa Satnit."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wifs/ kas no tan \nNamna Durwinm ahra iseeg/ ta \npascha Affins laid us winna Ga \nwu paleek/ un mehs buhſim ni \nnoseedsigi: Bet wifs/ kas pee te \nNamna buhs/ ta pascha Affin \nlaid us muhsu Galwu palee \nja kas faru Rohku pee win \npeeliks."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ja tu scho muh \nDarbusinnainu darrifi/ tad bu \nſim mehs nenoseedsigi tan \nSwehreschanâ/ fo tu mums e \nlikufi swehrecht."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija winna: E \ntas ta paleek/ ka juhs fakfa \nTad atlade winna tohs neh \nun tee aisgahje/ un winna peeje \nto farkann Wirwi pee ta Loha"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta aisgahje tee/ un nal \nKalnôs/ un palikte tur trihs De \nna"
    }
  ],
